## --------------------------------------------------------------  ##
##                                                                 ##
##  Heroku centric slugignore which removes unnecessary items      ##
##  from being included in the release.                            ##
##  @link: https://devcenter.heroku.com/articles/slug-compiler     ##
##  @link: https://goo.gl/J4jmUB                                   ##
##                                                                 ##
##  General Guideline:                                             ##
##  Any file that isn't necessary for the application to run       ##
##  should be omitted via .slugignore. This includes tests, source ##
##  files that are used to generate static css/html/js files,      ##
##  and any files included in the .ignore.                         ##
##                                                                 ##
##                                                                 ##
## Updated 01/28/2018 - AB                                         ##
## --------------------------------------------------------------  ##


#             SOP FILES TO NEVER INCLUDE
# --------------------------------------------------  #
/.backup
/.idea
/.src
/test
/tests
.DS_Store
*.sql
.env
*.md
nginx_local.conf


#        BUILD DEPENDENCIES & DOCUMENTATION
# --------------------------------------------------  #
/vendor
/node_modules
package-lock.json
gulpfile.js
phpunit.xml



#       DEVELOPMENT & LOG FILES
# --------------------------------------------------  #
/.vagrant
Vagrantfile
vBootstrap.sh
/public/log
/UnitTests